-- U.S. Prudential's China fund JV to launch 10 bln yuan fund
-- 
-- Tue Aug 14, 2007 2:12am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/08/14/us-china-fund-prudential-idUSSHA17345120070814

 

 SHANGHAI  (Reuters) - U.S. insurer Prudential Financial's ( PRU.N ) fund management venture in China plans to launch a domestic A-share fund next Tuesday to raise up to 10 billion yuan ($1.32 billion), the venture's chief investment officer said. 

 The fund, whose launch was approved by Chinese securities regulators this month, will focus on large-cap stocks, James Yuan of the Shanghai-based joint venture, Everbright Pramerica, told Reuters.